University Medical Centre, P.O. Box 5800, 6202 AZ, Maastricht, The Netherlands.

Comment in
    Breast Cancer Res Treat. 2021 Nov;190(1):1.

PURPOSE: To provide an overview of model characteristics and outcomes of 
model-based economic evaluations concerning chemotherapy and targeted therapy 
(TT) for metastatic breast cancer (MBC); to assess the quality of the studies; 
to analyse the association between model characteristics and study quality and 
outcomes.
METHODS: PubMED and NHS EED were systematically searched. Inclusion criteria 
